emotionally blackmailed me

1:17:53.418 --> 1:17:55.253
into staying a few more days,

1:17:55.962 --> 1:17:57.297
what's the plan?

1:17:57.381 --> 1:17:58.340
Well…

1:17:59.508 --> 1:18:02.678
