1:18:42.384 --> 1:18:43.427
I…

1:18:44.177 --> 1:18:46.012
Amanda, you can trust me.

1:18:47.514 --> 1:18:48.432
You can feel safe.

1:18:48.932 --> 1:18:49.808
I mean…

1:18:50.308 --> 1:18:51.143
Unless…

1:18:52.978 --> 1:18:54.688
Please don't tell me you're a vegetarian

1:18:54.771 --> 1:18:55.939
I can't deal.

1:18:57.774 --> 1:18:58.942
Stop making me laugh.

1:19:00.193 --> 1:19:01.027
Um…

1:19:03.447 --> 1:19:04.614
So the thing is…

1:19:08.160 --> 1:19:09.202
I have a daughter.

1:19:10.662 --> 1:19:11.580
Alright.

1:19:14.332 --> 1:19:15.167
And?

1:19:15.709 --> 1:19:17.002
That's it.

1:19:17.085 --> 1:19:18.086
I have a daughter.

1:19:18.587 --> 1:19:19.796
I--

1:19:20.505 --> 1:19:21.465
I… I

1:19:22.174 --> 1:19:23.675
I don't understand, what…

1:19:24.634 --> 1:19:26.386
What are you expecting?

1:19:26.470 --> 1:19:28.972
That's meant to be a
deal breaker for guys right?

1:19:31.349 --> 1:19:32.851
What guys have you been hanging out with?

1:19:32.934 --> 1:19:34.269
Are you serious?

1:19:34.352 --> 1:19:36.229
Is this a Nigerian thing?

1:19:36.313 --> 1:19:38.565
