who you've been spending your time with,

1:19:48.784 --> 1:19:50.118
because this doesn't make sense to me.

1:19:50.202 --> 1:19:51.077
It's like…

1:19:52.954 --> 1:19:54.706
my opinion of…

1:19:55.207 --> 1:19:56.249
kind of questioning.

1:19:56.333 --> 1:19:57.834
