Chimnoram.

1:20:01.838 --> 1:20:02.672
Chim…

1:20:03.632 --> 1:20:04.591
Can I just say "Nora"?

1:20:04.674 --> 1:20:05.759
Yeah

1:20:06.843 --> 1:20:09.805
