1:20:12.599 --> 1:20:15.894
"As long as God is in control,
everything will be okay".

1:20:17.938 --> 1:20:18.897
It's deep.

1:20:20.315 --> 1:20:22.067
Wish I had a Nigerian name,

1:20:22.150 --> 1:20:23.235
could be Nigerian…

1:20:24.277 --> 1:20:26.571
-I guess I'd have to be black first right?
-Yes, that.

1:20:27.113 --> 1:20:28.448
There is that…

1:20:30.325 --> 1:20:31.284
Nora.

1:20:32.577 --> 1:20:33.787
I guess she's a lovely girl.

1:20:34.663 --> 1:20:35.580
Just like her mum.

1:20:41.461 --> 1:20:42.295
What?

1:20:44.673 --> 1:20:46.800
You had me thinking
we were going to be out,

1:20:46.883 --> 1:20:48.969
burying a body together or something.

1:20:49.052 --> 1:20:51.555
And then I find out you have a daughter.

1:20:52.764 --> 1:20:53.765
You're weird.

1:20:56.935 --> 1:20:57.978
No, come here, come here.

1:20:59.271 --> 1:21:00.313
I want to be…

1:21:00.856 --> 1:21:02.983
A part of, each and
every part of your life.

1:21:04.067 --> 1:21:04.901
In totality.

1:21:07.988 --> 1:21:08.822
Come here.

1:21:15.370 --> 1:21:17.122
You're going to make me cry.

1:21:20.125 --> 1:21:21.084
Let's go.

1:22:23.021 --> 1:22:24.022
Fine day isn't it?

1:22:24.105 --> 1:22:24.940
Yeah.

1:22:26.024 --> 1:22:26.900
It's beautiful.

1:22:28.151 --> 1:22:28.985
Right?

1:22:29.527 --> 1:22:31.404
-This is us, my old and faithful.
-Oh

1:22:33.239 --> 1:22:34.115
Texas?

1:22:36.117 --> 1:22:37.035
Long story.

1:22:37.953 --> 1:22:39.037
Let's go get your bag.

1:22:39.120 --> 1:22:39.955
Okay.

1:22:44.709 --> 1:22:45.627
Alright.

1:22:47.796 --> 1:22:50.048
-So gentlemanly…
-There you go, I do what I can.

1:22:50.131 --> 1:22:51.091
Thank you.

1:22:53.385 --> 1:22:56.596
Let's just take a ride along the bay

1:22:58.223 --> 1:23:02.268
We don't need to work
We can sit around and play

1:23:02.352 --> 1:23:06.106
After waiting for so long to get away

1:23:07.607 --> 1:23:12.362
Baby don't hold back,
All you gotta do is say

1:23:12.445 --> 1:23:18.868
What would you like
To be satisfied with me

1:23:20.537 --> 1:23:25.125
I've been counting moments of love

1:23:25.208 --> 1:23:29.754
