To be satisfied with me

1:23:44.811 --> 1:23:46.938
Um, how much further are we going?

1:23:47.605 --> 1:23:48.815
Oh, we'll be there soon.

1:23:50.608 --> 1:23:52.402
My little slice of heaven,
you're gonna love it.

1:23:53.486 --> 1:23:54.988
Why do you think so?

1:23:57.824 --> 1:24:01.119
So, you remember that blog entry
you wrote about your bucket list?

1:24:01.619 --> 1:24:03.580
And on it, there was cabin in the woods.

1:24:03.663 --> 1:24:05.749
Have you really read all my blog posts?

1:24:05.832 --> 1:24:06.958
Of course.

1:24:08.668 --> 1:24:10.336
Look, I think you're a great writer.

1:24:11.504 --> 1:24:12.505
To be honest,

1:24:13.214 --> 1:24:15.675
I'm kind of hoping you might
write an article while we're here.

1:24:16.676 --> 1:24:18.053
Witness greatness at work.

1:24:19.179 --> 1:24:21.639
Be careful what you wish for

1:24:21.723 --> 1:24:22.724
Yeah…

1:24:23.933 --> 1:24:25.351
‎Alright.

1:24:26.144 --> 1:24:27.520
That's what I'm talking about.

1:24:27.604 --> 1:24:29.606
Finger crossed, no promises.

1:24:29.689 --> 1:24:31.024
Okay.

1:24:31.107 --> 1:24:32.484
You get me all excited now.

1:24:32.567 --> 1:24:35.904
We've been drinking
Champagne on the beach of Malibu

1:24:37.655 --> 1:24:39.824
Cruising down the boulevard

1:24:39.908 --> 1:24:43.286
Kissing in the back seat of the car

1:24:44.120 --> 1:24:47.040
Making love under the stars

1:24:47.123 --> 1:24:53.505
How would you like
To be satisfied with me

1:24:55.173 --> 1:24:59.761
I've been counting moments of love

1:24:59.844 --> 1:25:04.474
I've been catching signs from above

1:25:04.557 --> 1:25:08.770
All I wanna do is satisfy you

1:25:09.395 --> 1:25:16.152
Baby all you want is
To be satisfied with me

1:25:16.236 --> 1:25:17.946
It's like the middle of nowhere.

1:25:18.446 --> 1:25:19.656
Don't like the mountains?

1:25:20.240 --> 1:25:21.950
-It's beautiful right?
-New experience.

1:25:23.785 --> 1:25:24.786
Alright.

1:25:24.869 --> 1:25:27.747
All I wanna do is satisfy you

1:25:28.581 --> 1:25:35.255
Baby all you want is
To be satisfied with me

1:25:37.757 --> 1:25:38.675
After you.

1:25:41.845 --> 1:25:43.555
Whoa.

1:25:47.600 --> 1:25:50.311
This is another romcom cliché but…

1:25:53.857 --> 1:25:55.483
Welcome to my humble abode.

1:25:58.111 --> 1:25:58.945
So…

1:26:00.155 --> 1:26:01.114
Nice.

1:26:04.117 --> 1:26:05.076
Whoa…

1:26:07.704 --> 1:26:08.872
Wow…

1:26:11.875 --> 1:26:14.210
That's a lot of dead animals.

1:26:15.628 --> 1:26:18.214
Well, I can't take credit for all of them.

1:26:19.299 --> 1:26:20.341
But it's home.

1:26:29.475 --> 1:26:31.269
No, no, no… It's okay, it's okay.

1:26:31.811 --> 1:26:32.729
It's just Edna.

1:26:33.438 --> 1:26:34.689
She…

1:26:34.772 --> 1:26:36.107
She takes care of the house for me.

1:26:36.191 --> 1:26:37.108
Oh…

1:26:37.192 --> 1:26:39.569
She's known me since I was an errant teen.

1:26:40.403 --> 1:26:42.614
Edna, you can not be
sneaking up on us like that.

1:26:42.697 --> 1:26:43.698
No, it's okay.

1:26:43.781 --> 1:26:45.283
It's okay… she…

1:26:45.366 --> 1:26:46.534
It's fine, no problem.

1:26:47.202 --> 1:26:48.620
So you're taking her side now?

1:26:50.246 --> 1:26:51.122
Edna?

1:26:51.915 --> 1:26:54.542
This is Amanda, she's our guest.

1:26:55.293 --> 1:26:56.586
Nice to meet you ma.

1:26:57.587 --> 1:26:59.088
Um… Edna.

1:27:06.888 --> 1:27:08.932
