she doesn't have anyone.

1:27:16.022 --> 1:27:16.898
She's like me.

1:27:16.981 --> 1:27:18.233
Aww…

1:27:19.275 --> 1:27:20.985
But, let's get you moved in.

1:30:31.968 --> 1:30:34.345
For all the pain that you have caused me.

1:30:35.680 --> 1:30:40.935
That child you're carrying
will cause you so much pain.

1:30:41.477 --> 1:30:43.396
So much more.

1:30:43.479 --> 1:30:46.274
So much more pain.

1:30:46.357 --> 1:30:48.109
More.

1:31:14.594 --> 1:31:16.512
No, no, no…

1:31:21.934 --> 1:31:23.394
More…

1:31:25.521 --> 1:31:26.439
What happened?

1:31:29.400 --> 1:31:30.943
I had a nightmare.

1:31:32.987 --> 1:31:34.030
Come here.

1:31:38.159 --> 1:31:39.118
Do you want to talk about it?

1:31:55.051 --> 1:31:57.261
So what your father said….

1:31:57.345 --> 1:31:58.221
The curse.

1:32:00.556 --> 1:32:02.767
