serious emotional damage.

1:32:09.523 --> 1:32:11.150
Sometimes I…

1:32:15.071 --> 1:32:16.447
My daughter Nora…

1:32:20.076 --> 1:32:24.247
I feel like maybe my dad's
curse is in effect, you know?

1:32:24.997 --> 1:32:29.543
She's always so moody
and so defiant, like I…

1:32:31.921 --> 1:32:33.256
I think she hates me.

1:32:33.839 --> 1:32:36.550
That's just a teenager, it's normal.

1:32:37.051 --> 1:32:38.094
They're always abnormal.

1:32:40.721 --> 1:32:42.348
What your dad said, that's…

1:32:45.142 --> 1:32:47.895
That's just the pained words
of a control freak parent.

1:32:48.938 --> 1:32:51.524
What you want to do,
what you want to believe,

1:32:52.483 --> 1:32:53.609
that's all that matters.

1:33:00.241 --> 1:33:01.158
Thank you.

1:33:01.701 --> 1:33:02.785
Doctor Phil.

1:33:03.452 --> 1:33:04.662
You're welcome ma'am.

1:33:06.372 --> 1:33:08.499
-I think I'm more a Tony Robbins guy.
-Um-hmm…

1:33:09.250 --> 1:33:10.835
-I hear you.
-Yeah.

1:33:25.891 --> 1:33:27.435
It has been,

1:33:28.185 --> 1:33:29.186
so long…

1:33:30.146 --> 1:33:31.439
