1:33:52.293 --> 1:33:53.669
I can take care of you.

1:33:56.213 --> 1:33:57.089
You complete me.

1:33:57.882 --> 1:33:59.258
I'm never letting you go.

1:34:00.217 --> 1:34:01.052
Never.

