1:34:28.537 --> 1:34:31.540
Aww… so romantic.

1:34:31.624 --> 1:34:32.833
You just relax here.

1:35:01.278 --> 1:35:02.696
-Go…
-Jesus!

1:35:05.324 --> 1:35:06.784
Good evening Edna.

1:35:07.827 --> 1:35:08.828
Go…

1:35:24.427 --> 1:35:25.719
Ah…

1:35:27.054 --> 1:35:28.556
I hope you enjoyed dinner?

1:35:28.639 --> 1:35:29.723
I did.

1:35:30.224 --> 1:35:31.267
Thank you.

1:35:31.350 --> 1:35:32.184
Yeah.

1:35:35.146 --> 1:35:37.815
So when are we leaving for
the airport tomorrow morning?

1:35:39.275 --> 1:35:41.235
It's a long way out here.

1:35:41.735 --> 1:35:43.446
I don't want to be late for my flight.

1:35:45.114 --> 1:35:45.990
Well…

1:35:48.409 --> 1:35:50.035
I was hoping you'd stay a little longer.

1:35:51.537 --> 1:35:52.538
Seriously.

1:35:52.621 --> 1:35:55.166
Whatever the charge
is to change it, I'll take care of it.

1:35:57.835 --> 1:35:59.003
Actually,

1:36:01.630 --> 1:36:04.758
I originally booked
two weeks for this trip.

1:36:04.842 --> 1:36:06.218
-But…
-No buts.

1:36:06.302 --> 1:36:07.720
My travel agent will handle it.

1:36:08.220 --> 1:36:10.389
But Nora.

1:36:11.974 --> 1:36:13.809
I need to get back to my daughter.

1:36:14.477 --> 1:36:15.978
