1:36:22.234 --> 1:36:23.486
No…

1:36:23.569 --> 1:36:24.570
-Alright
-Come on.

1:36:24.653 --> 1:36:25.529
Alright.

1:36:27.198 --> 1:36:28.741
We'll leave first thing in the morning.

1:36:29.325 --> 1:36:30.743
There you go.

1:36:30.826 --> 1:36:33.245
