1:36:55.518 --> 1:36:56.352
‎Yeah.

1:36:58.395 --> 1:36:59.855
Are you okay?

1:36:59.939 --> 1:37:00.773
I'm fine.

1:37:00.856 --> 1:37:03.484
I just had a little bit too much.

1:37:04.151 --> 1:37:04.985
Amanda!

1:37:14.119 --> 1:37:15.788
Thank God, you're awake.

1:37:20.251 --> 1:37:21.585
Come here.

1:37:24.004 --> 1:37:24.838
Edna.

1:37:24.922 --> 1:37:27.383
You have to stop scaring
my guest, please leave.

1:37:31.637 --> 1:37:32.513
I'm sorry about that.

1:37:33.973 --> 1:37:35.099
How are you feeling?

1:37:40.437 --> 1:37:41.564
My head hurts.

1:37:43.566 --> 1:37:44.775
What time is it?

1:37:45.609 --> 1:37:46.610
It's about 9am.

1:37:47.820 --> 1:37:51.156
-My flight
-No, no… you can't…

1:37:51.740 --> 1:37:53.200
You can't go on a trip right now.

1:37:54.535 --> 1:37:55.744
I've called my doctor.

1:37:55.828 --> 1:37:57.413
He's on his way down to see you now.

1:37:57.496 --> 1:37:59.039
-Yes, but I--
-I understand

1:37:59.123 --> 1:38:00.499
I understand, I do.

1:38:00.583 --> 1:38:03.127
You can't go on a long
trip right now, I won't allow it.

1:38:04.420 --> 1:38:05.462
I'm going to get you better.

1:38:05.963 --> 1:38:08.465
Okay, you'll be back
on your feet in no time.

1:38:09.049 --> 1:38:10.593
You can jet off to see your Nora.

1:38:10.676 --> 1:38:12.094
Yes but… I--

1:38:13.804 --> 1:38:15.222
Here, here… water

1:38:16.098 --> 1:38:17.141
Water.

1:38:20.311 --> 1:38:21.353
Drink.

1:38:23.230 --> 1:38:24.231
There you go.

1:38:25.983 --> 1:38:26.859
Is it better?

1:38:27.818 --> 1:38:28.652
Yeah.

1:38:28.736 --> 1:38:29.612
Good…

1:38:32.531 --> 1:38:33.782
Rest sweetheart.

1:38:34.491 --> 1:38:36.327
I'll make you some chicken soup, okay.

1:39:31.006 --> 1:39:33.342
Look what we have here.

1:39:35.719 --> 1:39:37.221
A few servings of this…

1:39:38.263 --> 1:39:39.682
You'll be better in no time.

