1:39:45.229 --> 1:39:46.188
I got you soup.

1:39:47.314 --> 1:39:48.899
Wake up I got you soup.

1:39:49.608 --> 1:39:50.484
Come on

1:39:51.110 --> 1:39:52.236
You need to sit up.

1:39:53.737 --> 1:39:55.155
Come on.

1:39:55.739 --> 1:39:56.907
I got you.

1:39:58.242 --> 1:39:59.702
Here we go.

1:40:00.661 --> 1:40:01.704
Now…

1:40:05.332 --> 1:40:06.792
Ready and…

1:40:08.168 --> 1:40:09.211
in…

1:40:10.337 --> 1:40:11.213
Come on.

1:40:15.259 --> 1:40:16.635
I'm only going to say this once.

1:40:17.177 --> 1:40:20.889
You're not to come in here until I
say otherwise, do you understand?

1:40:29.231 --> 1:40:30.524
Here we go.

1:40:30.607 --> 1:40:31.483
Please…

1:40:32.901 --> 1:40:35.154
Please, take me back to--

1:40:35.237 --> 1:40:37.281
I will.

1:40:37.364 --> 1:40:38.991
But you have to get well first.

1:40:39.074 --> 1:40:40.284
-Yes, please.
-Yes.

1:40:40.367 --> 1:40:43.036
-I need to… please.
-I know, I know, sit, sit.

1:40:43.120 --> 1:40:44.288
-Relax…
-You're stressing me.

1:40:44.371 --> 1:40:46.331
Stressing will not make it any better.

1:40:47.249 --> 1:40:48.500
-I need to get--
-Here, here, here…

1:40:49.168 --> 1:40:50.294
Back, back.

1:40:50.377 --> 1:40:52.337
Got you. Have some.

1:40:52.421 --> 1:40:53.589
Here we go.

1:40:53.672 --> 1:40:54.923
Come on, come on.

1:40:55.591 --> 1:40:56.800
That's it

1:40:56.884 --> 1:40:58.427
You're going to be okay.

1:40:58.969 --> 1:41:00.554
You're going to be okay.

1:41:02.181 --> 1:41:03.265
There you go.

1:41:03.348 --> 1:41:05.350
There we go.

1:41:06.059 --> 1:41:07.478
Let me get the water.

1:41:09.730 --> 1:41:10.564
Have some water.

1:41:11.732 --> 1:41:12.733
Yeah.

1:41:13.525 --> 1:41:14.526
There…

1:41:14.610 --> 1:41:16.361
Now, just relax.

1:41:19.281 --> 1:41:20.574
You're going to be alright.

1:41:21.575 --> 1:41:23.118
I'm here to take care of you.

1:41:24.369 --> 1:41:26.121
I'll be here till the very end.

1:41:59.613 --> 1:42:01.114
Hey pumpkin, you're not sleeping?

1:42:01.198 --> 1:42:02.533
Have you spoken to mum?

1:42:02.616 --> 1:42:04.326
I've been calling her
but she's not answering.

1:42:04.409 --> 1:42:07.621
Nora, I'm sure she's
very busy. She's fine.

1:42:08.205 --> 1:42:09.998
Don't worry she'll call you tomorrow okay.

1:42:10.499 --> 1:42:11.333
Okay.

1:42:11.416 --> 1:42:14.753
Now, go grab some sleep
and stop worrying your pretty head.

1:42:15.879 --> 1:42:17.089
I love you.

1:42:22.010 --> 1:42:23.637
Hey… Amanda.

1:42:32.312 --> 1:42:33.272
Again?

1:42:41.071 --> 1:42:43.156
Babe, what's going on?

1:42:43.240 --> 1:42:45.617
What's up with this radio
silence? I don't understand.

1:42:45.701 --> 1:42:47.744
Nora and I have been
trying to reach you for like…

1:42:47.828 --> 1:42:49.288
…forever and nothing

1:42:49.371 --> 1:42:53.041
You didn't even think to send us
a simple message on WhatsApp.

1:42:53.542 --> 1:42:54.835
It doesn't make sense.

1:42:54.918 --> 1:42:58.005
You can't just meet a
man and forget about us.

1:42:58.088 --> 1:42:59.631
Is the "thing" really that good?

1:43:01.592 --> 1:43:03.468
Oh…

1:43:04.803 --> 1:43:06.221
Um…

1:43:07.306 --> 1:43:08.724
So, your mum came.

1:43:09.474 --> 1:43:11.101
And your sister.

1:43:11.852 --> 1:43:13.562
And they said something like…

1:43:14.062 --> 1:43:15.772
you blocked them.

1:43:17.065 --> 1:43:19.318
Babe, honestly I hope you're fine.

1:43:19.860 --> 1:43:22.696
Whatever it is, just
buzz us when you can, okay?

1:43:23.196 --> 1:43:24.781
And greet hubby for us.

1:43:25.949 --> 1:43:28.911
I miss you, I miss you.

1:43:33.332 --> 1:43:34.541
Bye…

1:43:59.942 --> 1:44:02.235
Baby, you're looking so much better today.

1:44:04.738 --> 1:44:06.073
It's time for soup.

1:44:06.156 --> 1:44:07.824
It's really helping you get better.

1:44:08.909 --> 1:44:09.785
-No…
-Come on.

1:44:09.868 --> 1:44:11.536
-Come on, I'll sit you up.
-No…

1:44:11.620 --> 1:44:12.537
Come on.

1:44:14.581 --> 1:44:16.166
-There we go.
-Babe…

1:44:16.249 --> 1:44:17.084
Yeah.

1:44:17.584 --> 1:44:19.044
Please take me back.

1:44:19.544 --> 1:44:22.255
You need to eat, you
need to regain your strength.

1:44:22.339 --> 1:44:24.925
Please, I need to go back.

1:44:25.676 --> 1:44:26.885
My daughter.

1:44:27.469 --> 1:44:29.513
They'll be worried about me.

1:44:29.596 --> 1:44:31.139
-Please.
-We'll go.

1:44:31.848 --> 1:44:32.724
We'll go.

1:44:34.142 --> 1:44:36.603
We just have to get you stronger.

1:44:37.604 --> 1:44:38.647
You promise?

1:44:39.690 --> 1:44:40.774
Cross my heart.

1:44:41.608 --> 1:44:42.567
I love you.

1:44:43.527 --> 1:44:44.444
Now come on.

1:44:45.278 --> 1:44:46.446
Just a little bit of soup.

1:45:36.830 --> 1:45:38.040
My phone…

1:45:49.092 --> 1:45:50.093
My phone.

1:46:09.613 --> 1:46:10.739
Edna?

1:46:11.573 --> 1:46:12.491
My phone.

1:46:14.076 --> 1:46:15.869
Please do you know where my phone is?

1:46:19.498 --> 1:46:21.083
Edna my phone.

1:46:37.474 --> 1:46:38.350
There you are.

1:46:39.309 --> 1:46:41.144
You had us worried, what happened?

1:46:41.770 --> 1:46:42.687
I saw her.

1:46:44.898 --> 1:46:46.066
I saw her.

1:46:46.983 --> 1:46:48.819
You saw who? Edna?

1:46:52.405 --> 1:46:53.240
Liz.

1:46:53.740 --> 1:46:54.741
I saw…

1:46:54.825 --> 1:46:55.700
I saw her.

1:46:55.784 --> 1:46:56.952
Liz?

1:47:02.290 --> 1:47:03.500
This is worse than I thought.

1:47:03.583 --> 1:47:05.127
You… you're hallucinating.

1:47:05.210 --> 1:47:06.086
No.

1:47:06.169 --> 1:47:07.629
Ask, Edna saw…

1:47:08.213 --> 1:47:09.339
Ask Edna.

1:47:11.007 --> 1:47:11.842
Edna…

1:47:17.764 --> 1:47:18.807
Was someone here?

1:47:21.476 --> 1:47:22.727
You saw her.

1:47:24.312 --> 1:47:25.438
You saw her.

1:47:25.522 --> 1:47:26.565
You saw her.

1:47:26.648 --> 1:47:28.650
We'll need to get you to a hospital.

1:47:30.944 --> 1:47:33.155
Please, my phone.

1:47:34.573 --> 1:47:35.782
Do you have it?

1:47:36.366 --> 1:47:37.576
Yes, it's with me.

1:47:38.160 --> 1:47:38.994
Okay.

1:47:40.036 --> 1:47:41.496
Please I need it.

1:47:42.122 --> 1:47:42.998
Okay.

1:47:43.081 --> 1:47:44.082
Give me a second.

1:47:55.927 --> 1:47:56.761
Michael.

1:47:58.013 --> 1:47:59.055
Michael, did…

1:47:59.139 --> 1:48:00.348
Did you lock the door?

1:48:01.183 --> 1:48:02.184
Back to bed dear.

1:48:03.226 --> 1:48:04.060
Michael.

1:48:05.937 --> 1:48:06.771
Please.

1:48:07.522 --> 1:48:08.899
Open the door.

1:48:09.608 --> 1:48:10.483
I can't.

1:48:12.444 --> 1:48:14.613
It's for your own safety,
you're hallucinating now.

1:48:14.696 --> 1:48:16.865
Michael, you don't know that.

1:48:16.948 --> 1:48:20.202
You're not a doctor, I
need a doctor please.

1:48:21.036 --> 1:48:22.579
I used to be a paramedic.

1:48:22.662 --> 1:48:23.955
I know a thing or two.

1:48:24.039 --> 1:48:25.749
Oh, let me out…

1:48:25.832 --> 1:48:28.168
Please, let me out.

1:48:30.086 --> 1:48:31.421
Please…

1:48:31.922 --> 1:48:33.673
Get some rest dear.

1:48:39.095 --> 1:48:41.181
Please…

1:48:45.227 --> 1:48:47.562
Please, let me out.

1:49:15.173 --> 1:49:16.383
Michael.

1:49:17.467 --> 1:49:18.301
Michael.

1:49:18.927 --> 1:49:20.053
Who's there?

1:49:46.288 --> 1:49:47.247
No time…

1:49:47.330 --> 1:49:50.166
Quick, come, come…

1:50:35.879 --> 1:50:36.963
Edna?

1:50:37.756 --> 1:50:39.090
Edna.

1:50:42.844 --> 1:50:44.804
Edna.

1:50:54.272 --> 1:50:57.025
Hey, please you need to be quiet.

1:50:57.108 --> 1:50:59.027
I'm trying to help you.

1:50:59.110 --> 1:51:01.571
Your life is in danger, we
need to get out of here now.

1:51:02.364 --> 1:51:05.617
Several women, mostly Nigerian,
arrive the states then disappear.

1:51:06.201 --> 1:51:07.827
Michael is our prime suspect.

1:51:07.911 --> 1:51:11.539
They can all be traced to him as the
last contact before he went missing.

1:51:11.623 --> 1:51:12.749
He is sick.

1:51:12.832 --> 1:51:15.001
We need to get out of here now. Before--

1:51:15.085 --> 1:51:15.919
Don't move!

1:51:17.504 --> 1:51:18.588
What's going on.

1:51:20.382 --> 1:51:23.093
I’m detective Sanders
and you’re under arrest.

1:51:23.843 --> 1:51:25.345
Arrest? But what for?

1:51:25.428 --> 1:51:27.430
The kidnapping of Amanda Abraham.

1:51:28.348 --> 1:51:29.307
Don't be ridiculous.

1:51:29.391 --> 1:51:32.310
I will shoot you if you
move any closer right now.

1:51:36.272 --> 1:51:39.984
Like Amanda, most of the women you
bring here are never heard from again.

1:51:40.610 --> 1:51:42.278
-You killed them.
-What!

1:51:42.362 --> 1:51:43.947
Get on your knees.

1:51:44.572 --> 1:51:45.615
Amanda.

1:51:46.157 --> 1:51:47.075
Are you okay?

1:51:47.158 --> 1:51:49.244
-Did she hurt you?
-Get on your knees.

1:51:49.327 --> 1:51:51.287
Don't be afraid,
it's all going to be fine.

1:51:51.371 --> 1:51:52.747
But don't listen to her.

1:51:53.289 --> 1:51:56.709
I had some of my guys
look into her she's a nutcase.

1:51:56.793 --> 1:51:58.420
-Shut up.
-She obsesses over men,

1:51:58.503 --> 1:51:59.504
She stalks them…

1:51:59.587 --> 1:52:01.589
-Shut up.
-some of them have been killed.

1:52:01.673 --> 1:52:03.133
That badge is fake.

1:52:03.216 --> 1:52:05.343
He's lying…I to--

1:52:14.727 --> 1:52:15.812
Stay down.

1:54:22.730 --> 1:54:23.773
No time.

1:54:24.274 --> 1:54:25.525
Quick.

1:54:30.738 --> 1:54:33.283
Sweetie… where are you going?

1:54:33.366 --> 1:54:34.409
Go.

1:54:34.492 --> 1:54:35.618
Edna.

1:54:38.705 --> 1:54:40.039
After all I’ve done for you.

1:54:40.123 --> 1:54:42.041
Keeping you on when no one else would.

1:54:42.125 --> 1:54:43.001
Go.

1:54:43.084 --> 1:54:44.210
No time, go!

1:54:44.294 --> 1:54:47.005
-I'm not going without you Edna.
-You trust her?

1:54:48.631 --> 1:54:50.592
You trust her more than you trust me?

1:54:51.968 --> 1:54:54.137
She's been there for
every one of the girls.

1:54:55.221 --> 1:54:56.764
She's my family.

1:54:58.975 --> 1:55:00.393
I'm the only family she has.

1:55:00.476 --> 1:55:02.437
Say what you want.

1:55:02.937 --> 1:55:05.732
You will not kill this girl too.

1:55:06.900 --> 1:55:09.110
You, you'll have to go through me.

1:55:09.193 --> 1:55:10.695
What will you do?

1:55:11.279 --> 1:55:12.113
Hmm?

1:55:12.196 --> 1:55:13.740
Amanda, go.

1:55:13.823 --> 1:55:17.410
Come back to me and we'll
be normal again. I promise.

1:55:17.493 --> 1:55:20.204
Nothing is normal with us.

1:55:20.288 --> 1:55:22.373
You make me do evil.

1:55:22.916 --> 1:55:25.293
Because I have no choice.

1:55:26.628 --> 1:55:28.880
It stops now.

1:55:50.568 --> 1:55:51.903
Amanda!

1:56:08.086 --> 1:56:10.004
Amanda!

1:56:14.550 --> 1:56:16.094
Amanda!

1:56:18.346 --> 1:56:20.181
Amanda!

1:56:32.610 --> 1:56:34.821
There's no one else out here but us.

1:56:35.530 --> 1:56:38.199
You can go on for days
and not get anywhere.

1:56:40.702 --> 1:56:41.703
Amanda!

1:57:05.560 --> 1:57:07.270
I don't want to shoot you Amanda.

1:57:07.770 --> 1:57:10.189
I just want to talk, I
don't want to kill you.

1:57:11.858 --> 1:57:13.484
Amanda!

1:57:21.743 --> 1:57:24.078
I hoped, I really prayed.

1:57:25.705 --> 1:57:27.498
You said you would stay with me.

1:57:28.541 --> 1:57:30.418
I showed you nothing but love.

1:57:30.918 --> 1:57:33.337
and just like the
others, you want to leave me.

1:57:35.173 --> 1:57:37.633
Why am I so hard to love?

1:57:38.718 --> 1:57:40.970
Why are you leaving after all we shared?

1:57:48.811 --> 1:57:49.645
Don't move.

1:57:50.521 --> 1:57:51.689
I love you.

1:57:52.190 --> 1:57:53.399
I swear it.

1:57:56.277 --> 1:57:58.404
Don't cry, no, no, no…

1:57:58.488 --> 1:57:59.363
Don't cry.

1:57:59.447 --> 1:58:01.282
I don't want to see you cry.

1:58:02.533 --> 1:58:04.035
You made me mad…

1:58:04.994 --> 1:58:06.746
because you made me kill Edna.

1:58:08.790 --> 1:58:10.708
She was all I had.

1:58:10.792 --> 1:58:12.418
And you made me kill her.

1:58:12.502 --> 1:58:13.878
But you know what?

1:58:14.921 --> 1:58:16.130
I'll forgive you.

1:58:16.631 --> 1:58:18.007
I'll forgive you.

1:58:18.508 --> 1:58:21.302
If you promise not to run away again.

1:58:21.844 --> 1:58:24.138
Okay, okay, I promise.

1:58:25.640 --> 1:58:27.225
I'll get rid of the gun.

1:58:27.975 --> 1:58:29.602
-You promise?
-I promise.

1:58:30.478 --> 1:58:31.854
I promise.

1:58:34.190 --> 1:58:35.525
Can you see?

1:58:35.608 --> 1:58:37.193
I knew you'll come back.

2:00:12.205 --> 2:00:13.289
You forgot me.

2:00:13.372 --> 2:00:16.292
Don't worry, just let it happen.

2:00:16.375 --> 2:00:18.044
This time you won't wake up.

2:01:09.428 --> 2:01:12.431
He's been linked to the
disappearance of over fifteen women.

2:01:12.515 --> 2:01:13.349
What?

2:01:13.432 --> 2:01:14.809
Most of them Nigerian.

2:01:15.643 --> 2:01:18.354
Most of them we will discover
when forensics is done.

2:01:18.437 --> 2:01:21.107
They lye in those shallow graves
that you noticed in the woods.

2:01:25.236 --> 2:01:29.782
So, did he get them all
through his touring company?

2:01:30.283 --> 2:01:31.742
He never owned a touring company.

2:01:32.952 --> 2:01:34.537
We've arrested a couple of men who he paid

2:01:34.620 --> 2:01:35.955
to make women believe he's rich.

2:01:36.038 --> 2:01:37.373
He doesn't own anything.

2:01:38.082 --> 2:01:39.208
This cabin…

2:01:39.292 --> 2:01:41.168
belongs to the first victim he killed.

2:01:41.252 --> 2:01:43.087
Thanks to Liz's

2:01:43.170 --> 2:01:45.464
passion and doggedness

2:01:46.132 --> 2:01:48.467
this could have gone on for much longer.

2:01:49.635 --> 2:01:51.762
So is there anyone else
that you've seen with him?

2:01:51.846 --> 2:01:54.223
Anyone at all that could be in on this.

2:01:56.142 --> 2:01:59.770
Apart from Edna, he
did say he had no family.

2:01:59.854 --> 2:02:01.480
No, he never had family.

2:02:01.981 --> 2:02:04.150
He grew up in an orphanage
that he fled from as a teenager

2:02:04.233 --> 2:02:07.028
to avoid therapy sessions and
treatments for his mental disorder.

2:02:07.695 --> 2:02:09.905
Oh my goodness.

2:02:12.325 --> 2:02:13.409
Wait…

2:02:13.492 --> 2:02:15.870
There was a lady I met
with him in New York.

2:02:17.538 --> 2:02:19.832
He said that she was he's cousin, Natasha.

2:02:19.915 --> 2:02:21.000
Not a blood relative.

2:02:21.083 --> 2:02:22.668
They grew up in the orphanage together.

2:02:22.752 --> 2:02:25.004
That's what they called each other
at the orphanage "cousins"

2:02:25.087 --> 2:02:26.213
Yeah, we've spoken to her.

2:02:26.297 --> 2:02:28.424
She's given us the back
story on his time there.

2:02:29.383 --> 2:02:31.093
She's terribly shocked by all this,

2:02:31.177 --> 2:02:33.262
and swears she thought he
was in treatment this whole time.

2:02:34.013 --> 2:02:35.348
Wow.

2:02:35.848 --> 2:02:36.849
So…

2:02:37.350 --> 2:02:38.684
Why Nigerian women?

2:02:40.061 --> 2:02:42.355
Well, we're still gathering information

2:02:42.438 --> 2:02:44.148
but we've contacted the Nigerian Embassy.

2:02:44.231 --> 2:02:45.983
They are on standby
to take care of whatever

2:02:46.067 --> 2:02:48.027
it is that you might need
before you return home.

2:02:49.362 --> 2:02:51.197
Thank you so much.

2:02:51.280 --> 2:02:52.907
Thank you so, so much.

2:02:53.491 --> 2:02:55.242
Is there anything else I
can do for you right now?

2:02:57.661 --> 2:02:58.871
I need to get this.

2:02:59.372 --> 2:03:00.831
Excuse me.

2:03:05.294 --> 2:03:06.337
Hello babe.

2:03:06.962 --> 2:03:07.797
Hello.

2:03:07.880 --> 2:03:11.092
Babe, what's going on?
Why did you just abandon everybody?

2:03:11.175 --> 2:03:12.259
Was the "thing" really that good?

2:03:12.343 --> 2:03:13.886
Long story.

2:03:13.969 --> 2:03:15.596
Can I talk to Nora please?

2:03:16.180 --> 2:03:18.057
Wait…

2:03:18.140 --> 2:03:19.308
Babe are you okay?

2:03:19.934 --> 2:03:22.395
Look, I'll gist you later,
can I just talk to my baby?

2:03:22.978 --> 2:03:24.855
Yeah, yeah… hold on.

2:03:25.398 --> 2:03:26.232
Mummy.

2:03:26.816 --> 2:03:27.983
Hello.

2:03:28.567 --> 2:03:29.735
Mummy are you okay?

2:03:29.819 --> 2:03:32.613
Mummy I'm so sorry, I've
been worried about you.

2:03:33.614 --> 2:03:36.325
I love you so, so much.

2:03:37.201 --> 2:03:39.829
I'm sorry too, I miss you.

2:03:42.790 --> 2:03:43.874
I'm coming home.

2:03:53.509 --> 2:03:54.427
Ah-ah…

2:03:54.510 --> 2:03:56.971
-Look at this. Oh, that is lovely.
-Oh my God.

2:03:57.054 --> 2:03:58.514
-You like?
-This is beautiful.

2:03:58.597 --> 2:04:00.641
-Eh, I like it too.
-Oh…

